red-stock</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 购买了近 1.7 亿美元的比特币，其中大约一半是通过永久优先股融资的，这是自 11 月以来的最高比例。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iYOMFq2GBASs/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Feb 2026 16:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-17/saylor-s-strategy-buys-more-bitcoin-using-preferred-stock</guid></item></channel></rss>